309
00:16:39.466 --> 00:16:41.901
I'm looking into
Captain Smith's death.

310
00:16:42.034 --> 00:16:44.437
Oh. Nice to meet you.

311
00:16:47.840 --> 00:16:51.344
If. uh. if you're here.
I guess that means. uh...

312
00:16:51.411 --> 00:16:53.413
Yeah.

313
00:16:53.513 --> 00:16:55.415
He didn't have a family.

314
00:16:55.548 --> 00:16:58.217
I've got to get him dressed
and take him up to Arlington.

315
00:17:06.326 --> 00:17:08.661
