319
00:17:26.212 --> 00:17:29.616
Captain Smith was
Explosives Ordinance Disposal.

320
00:17:30.417 --> 00:17:33.252
Um. I guess. Is that important?

321
00:17:35.154 --> 00:17:36.423
It might be.

322
00:17:41.928 --> 00:17:45.298
