344
00:18:46.325 --> 00:18:49.529
It was so nuts.
I performed an MRI to be sure.

345
00:18:51.364 --> 00:18:54.867
That is highly abnormal.

346
00:18:55.968 --> 00:18:57.003
GREEN:
And it's not from the explosion?

347
00:18:57.103 --> 00:18:59.606
Mm-mmm.
Too symmetrical.

348
00:18:59.706 --> 00:19:01.508
