358
00:19:24.497 --> 00:19:26.833
He... he-he would never...

359
00:19:26.933 --> 00:19:29.736
We thought the same thing
until we did some more digging.

360
00:19:29.869 --> 00:19:32.071
and it turns out that

361
00:19:32.171 --> 00:19:34.441
