it-it'll work this time.

384
00:20:37.103 --> 00:20:38.938
Please.

385
00:20:40.607 --> 00:20:41.974
No.

386
00:20:51.551 --> 00:20:54.420
Y-Your daughter was very. um...

387
00:20:58.124 --> 00:21:00.793
I'm sorry. I know that's...

388
00:21:02.862 --> 00:21:05.798
That's-that's what
I want to say. is I'm sorry.

389
00:21:11.403 --> 00:21:13.372
A-Are you-are you comfortable?
Do you need anything?

390
00:21:13.472 --> 00:21:15.708
Maybe like...
water or. I don't...

391
