416
00:22:27.980 --> 00:22:31.050
The very same agency.
coincidentally. that caught you.

417
00:22:31.150 --> 00:22:33.152
Because you went off
the reservation. didn't you?

418
00:22:33.285 --> 00:22:34.553
LEWIS:
Ms. Ryan. that's completely unfounded.

419
00:22:34.621 --> 00:22:36.288
VOIT:
Wait. what is she talking...

420
00:22:36.388 --> 00:22:38.224
I'm sor... I don't know. What
di... Where did you hear that?

421
00:22:38.290 --> 00:22:40.426
