to people if...

463
00:24:25.597 --> 00:24:27.433
if-if... if they don't even
believe what I'm saying?

464
00:24:27.533 --> 00:24:30.703
I want to at least apologize
for what I actually did.

465
00:24:31.503 --> 00:24:33.973
All right. Let's-let's
think this thing through.

466
00:24:34.106 --> 00:24:37.609
You go on the record
