nothing high-tech.

480
00:25:10.576 --> 00:25:12.945
It can literally be. like.
a voice memo on your phone.

481
00:25:13.012 --> 00:25:14.680
- Why?
- Insurance.

482
00:25:14.781 --> 00:25:16.315
Voit wants to make sure
Brian doesn't edit him

483
00:25:16.415 --> 00:25:18.217
