493
00:25:38.604 --> 00:25:41.240
He's not. It's... (sighs)

494
00:25:41.340 --> 00:25:43.209
When Brian Garrity

495
00:25:43.309 --> 00:25:45.511
is in my life. it...

496
00:25:45.611 --> 00:25:47.179
Have you ever had heartburn?

497
00:25:47.279 --> 00:25:49.181
Where-where the...

498
00:25:49.281 --> 00:25:53.019
