505
00:26:08.667 --> 00:26:10.536
He already did.

506
00:26:10.636 --> 00:26:12.571
He had his own
counter-conditions.

507
00:26:12.671 --> 00:26:16.175
Ok... Okay. now I'm feeling it.

508
00:26:16.275 --> 00:26:17.376
(sighs) Come on.

509
00:26:17.509 --> 00:26:19.411
